{
  "stem": "25287.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came with horse and the bigger wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and not only us, and the three sister, my parents but whoever was able to fit in the big wagon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to the next city and then Satoraljaujhely we had the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we was in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe interesting to tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Next day or when we get to the synagogue, next day or the following day, the mayor wife sent down the butler and told the gendarme, the police, that I should go home with the police to give the material.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To-- so the butler came to the house, and the police came with me, and I give the material.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went-- went out from the apartment to the street with the police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my neighbor came and asked, Ilonka, would you like to give me something that I should hide it when you come back?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had-- not this one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When my fiance came down, ask my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm not going to wear the diamond ring, then I should wear this one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when he came back, he gave a new one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I put it off my, and I-- and I said to my neighbor, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If I don't come back-- because she have same age daughter like me-- then she can have it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But if I come back, I want it back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She give it back when I came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I give to my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my sister, my daughter when I get married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was a [? robbery. ?] So anyhow, this policeman, we walked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He said to me, Ilonka, I need to have a cup of coffee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I go to the coffee shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you said you would like to buy a folding cups.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
